This is my beloved baby and I am so proud of it! I am still using it, very high quality gaming machine, and it has aged beautifully. I am very passionate in maintaining it and I have learned a lot through using this beautiful machine. 
It has cost me serious capital to build it and I have also used the electrical surge protection equipment that I have previously purchased, during the lifetime of Desktop 1. 
This device came after a serious realization that any electronic device is an electrical device, first and foremost. And no matter how good a PC is, the performance of a device is not only dictated by the quality and the speed of its components, but also by the quality of the "juice", of the electricity flowing through that system. 
Once I have completely and solidly regulated the issue of electricity for all of my devices, my experience as a user of IT equipment has drastically changed. This, combined with an ever evolving maintenance protocol and routine, have brought me many moments of well earned joy, fun and learning experiences. 
I am still using this equipment, it has proved to be priceless and to provide my machines with the high quality juice that they deserve. 
